title: Adani Power, HDIL, HUDCO, IDFC Bank hit all-time low
content: Advanced Enzyme, IL&FS Transportation Networks, Inox Wind, Narayana Hrudayalaya and Navkar Corporation were among 9 stocks from the S&P BSE500 index hitting their respective all-time lows on the BSE.
